    "data_size": 200,
    "nom_orig": "Jun",
    "texte_orig": "That's[SP]right...[1205][001E][SP]We[SP]promised[SP]to[SP]protect[SP]Big\nSis[SP]together...[SP]forever...[1205][001E][SP]And[SP]I...[SP]I...![1205][001E]",
