    "data_size": 236,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "No[SP]matter[SP]who[SP]stands[SP]against[SP]you...[1205][001E][SP]Even[SP]if\nthe[SP]whole[SP]world[SP]becomes[SP]my[SP]enemy...[1205][001E][SP]I'll[SP]keep\nmy[SP]promise...",
